{"tha-ap522:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap522:0.2":"Phaladayakavagga ","tha-ap522:0.3":"10 Padumadharikattheraapadana ","tha-ap522:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap522:1.2":"romaso nama pabbato; ","tha-ap522:1.3":"Buddhopi sambhavo nama, ","tha-ap522:1.4":"abbhokase vasi tada. ","tha-ap522:2.1":"Bhavana nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap522:2.2":"padumam dharayim aham; ","tha-ap522:2.3":"Ekaham dharayitvana, ","tha-ap522:2.4":"bhavanam punaragamim. ","tha-ap522:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap522:3.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap522:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap522:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap522:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap522:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap522:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap522:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap522:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap522:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap522:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap522:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap522:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap522:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padumadhariko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap522:8.1":"Padumadharikattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap522:9.1":"Phaladayakavaggo dvepannasamo. ","tha-ap522:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap522:11.1":"Kuranciyam kapitthanca, ","tha-ap522:11.2":"kosambamatha ketakam; ","tha-ap522:11.3":"Nagapupphajjunanceva, ","tha-ap522:11.4":"kutaji ghosasannako. ","tha-ap522:12.1":"Thero ca sabbaphalado, ","tha-ap522:12.2":"tatha padumadhariko; ","tha-ap522:12.3":"Asiti cettha gathayo, ","tha-ap522:12.4":"tisso gatha taduttari. "}